Union & Cap Calculator U & ∩
```{r}
P_A <- 0.4
P_B <- 0.5

# Compute P(A ∩ B) for independent events
P_AB <- P_A * P_B

# Compute P(A ∪ B)
P_AUB <- P_A + P_B - P_AB

print(P_AUB)
```
