Confidence Interval
```{r}
size <- 10
mean <- 50
sd <- 8
conf_level <- 0.95

df <- size-1
t_crit <- qt(1 - (1 - conf_level)/2, df)
se <- sd / sqrt(size)
me <- t_crit * se

lower <- mean - me
upper <- mean + me
c(lower,upper)
```
